datalog_relationships:
is_conflicted(S) :- pc_member(S), subject_attribute(S, 'isConflicted', 'true').
is_eq_subjuserid_resuserid(S) :- pc_member(S), subject_attribute(S, 'isEq-subjUserId-resUserId', 'true').
subj_reviews_this_res_paper(S, R) :- pc_member(S), resource(R), subject_attribute(S, 'subjReviewsThisResPaper', 'true'), resource_attribute(R, 'paper', 'true').
has_submitted_review_for_res_paper(S, R) :- pc_member(S), resource(R), subject_attribute(S, 'hasSubmittedReviewForResPaper', 'true'), resource_attribute(R, 'paper', 'true').
phase_discussion(R) :- resource(R), resource_attribute(R, 'phase', 'discussion').
is_see_unassigned_allowed(R) :- resource(R), resource_attribute(R, 'isSeeUnassignedAllowed', 'true').
datalog_actions:
can_read(S, R) :- pc_member(S), resource(R), subject_attribute(S, 'role', 'pc-member'), subject_attribute(S, 'isConflicted', 'false'), action(S, 'read'), (is_eq_subjuserid_resuserid(S); phase_discussion(R); (subj_reviews_this_res_paper(S, R), has_submitted_review_for_res_paper(S, R)); is_see_unassigned_allowed(R)), not denied(S, R).
denied(S, R) :- pc_member(S), resource(R), not (is_eq_subjuserid_resuserid(S); phase_discussion(R); (subj_reviews_this_res_paper(S, R), has_submitted_review_for_res_paper(S, R)); is_see_unassigned_allowed(R)).

datalog_relationships:
has_role(S, 'subreviewer') :- Subject(S).
is_eq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R).
datalog_actions: can_create(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, 'subreviewer'), is_eq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, R).
